---
const faqs = [
  {
    q: "Do I need to be technical to use this?",
    a: "No. You need to paste one command into a terminal once, then talk to Claude normally. If you can copy-paste and type a sentence, you're set.",
  },
  {
    q: "Does it work with Claude Desktop, or only Claude Code?",
    a: "Both. The installer drops the skill into ~/.claude/skills/agentboard/ and wires the MCP server into Claude Desktop's config. Claude Code picks it up automatically on next session.",
  },
  {
    q: "Does my data leave my laptop?",
    a: "Never. AgentBoard runs on localhost. The whole thing — server, database, dashboard — is on your machine. There's no account, no telemetry, no cloud.",
  },
  {
    q: "Is it really free? What's the catch?",
    a: "Genuinely free, MIT licensed. No paid tier, no \"pro\" version. We wrote it because we wanted it to exist. The source is public.",
  },
  {
    q: "What platforms does it run on?",
    a: "macOS and Linux today, both Intel and Apple Silicon / ARM. Windows works via WSL; native Windows is on the roadmap.",
  },
  {
    q: "How do I uninstall it?",
    a: "Two commands: rm -rf ~/.agentboard ~/.claude/skills/agentboard, then remove the \"agentboard\" block from claude_desktop_config.json. Nothing else got installed, nothing else to clean up.",
  },
];
---

<section id="faq" class="relative border-t border-white/5 py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium text-zinc-500">Questions</p>
      <h2
        class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl"
      >
        Short answers.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <dl class="mt-14 divide-y divide-white/5 border-y border-white/5">
      {
        faqs.map((f) => (
          <div class="py-6 md:grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_1.6fr] md:gap-10">
            <dt class="text-base font-medium text-white">{f.q}</dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400 md:mt-0">
              {f.a}
            </dd>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </dl>

    <p class="mt-12 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500">
      Still stuck? <a
        href="https://github.com/anthropics"
        class="text-zinc-300 underline underline-offset-4 transition hover:text-white"
      >Open an issue on GitHub →</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
